  <p>If you did not request this password reset, just ignore this email and your password will stay the same.</p>

  <p>Big Dumb Web Dev</p>
  <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/andre-pictures/BDWD_email_icon.png" alt="Big Dumb Web Dev Logo" class="BDWD-icon">
